querylist.query: select a.*,b.name pname from codemst a join codemst b on a.parentcode=b.code where a.code like 'ch%' and a.compcode=@comp

datalist.mission:
기업의 효율적인 경영을 지원하기 위한 전산서비스를 제공한다.
당사의 서비스를 통해 기업들은 슬림한 조직을 기반으로 본업에 충실할 수 있다.

querylist.query: select top 40 * from achieveview2 where compcode=@comp and kpi='kp00000535' and yr=@yr

IF EXISTS (SELECT * FROM x WHERE tgtsegcode=@code)
BEGIN
update x
set custcode=@custcode
where tgtsegcode=@code
END
ELSE
BEGIN
insert x (tgtsegcode,custcode) values(@code,@custcode)
END
select a.*, divisiontype dvcode from daypilot a join compstaff b on a.staff=b.staffcode where comp=@comp
select * from codemst where code like 'dv%' and compcode=@comp

if exists(select * from codemst where code=@code)
update codemst
set parentcode=@pcode ,name=@name ,descript=@desc ,comp=@comp 
where code=@code
else
insert codemst (code,name,descript,parentcode,comp) values (@code,@name,@desc,@comp)

if exists (select * from tbimsi where code=@code)
begin
	update tbimsi
	set name=@name 
	where code=@code
end
else
begin 
	Insert tbimsi (code,name) values (@code,@name)
end

select a.code,name,parentcode,lat,lng from codemst a left outer join (select 'CH00000137'code,37.366905 lat,
          107693 lng union
select 'CH00000138',37.385997,127.119475 union
select 'CH00000139',37.575548,126.984747 union
select 'CH00000140',37.564820,126.966996 )b on a.code=b.code where a.code like 'ch%' and compcode=@comp

if exists (select * from comp where compcode=@comp)
update comp
compname=@compname ,postnum=@postnum ,address=@addr,
firstphone=@phone ,slogo=@slogo
where compcode=@comp
else
insert comp (compcode,compname,postnum,address,firstphone,slogo)
values (@comp,@compname,@postnum,@addr,@phone,@slogo)

select name,code,parentcode,'div'icon,compcode from codemst where code like 'dv%'
union

select a.*,b.name pname from codemst a join codemst b on a.parentcode=b.code where a.code like 'ch%'   and a.compcode=@comp

if exists (select * from codemst where code=@code)

where code=@code
else
insert codemst (code,name,parentcode,compcode) values (@code,@name,@pcode, @comp)
select code,name,parentcode from codemst where code like 'pd%' and compcode=@comp
select code,name,parentcode from codemst where code like 'pd%' and compcode='acuvue' and ( parentcode=@prod or code=@prod)
